Uses of Class
harrygpotter.tombola.tombolalib.TAward

  • Uses of TAward in harrygpotter.tombola.tombolalib

    Methods in harrygpotter.tombola.tombolalib that return TAward 
    Modifier and Type Method Description
    TAward TAwardList.getFirstAvailableAward()
    Return the first award object within the list that hasn't already been won by a card, null if all awards have been already appointed to cards.
    TAward TGame.getFirstAwardToResolve()
    When, during the tombola game, an award is contended by more than one card, that is, the game is paused in status "RESOLVING", this method returns the first award object within the ordered award list that have many contending cards.
    TAward TAwardList.getLastWonAward()
    Deprecated.
    Methods in harrygpotter.tombola.tombolalib that return types with arguments of type TAward 
    Modifier and Type Method Description
    java.util.List<TAward> TAwardList.getAvailableAwards()
    To be used during a tombola game, this method filters the current list of awards returning a new list containing only the still available ones.
    java.util.List<TAward> TAwardList.getWonsByExtractionCount​(int count)
    Return a list of TAward objects containing all the award won at the count-th extraction of the Tombola game.
    java.util.List<TAward> TAwardList.getWonsByExtractionNumber​(int number)
    Return a list of TAward objects containing all the award won with the extraction of the number passed as input parameter
    Methods in harrygpotter.tombola.tombolalib with parameters of type TAward 
    Modifier and Type Method Description
    boolean TAwardList.add​(TAward e)
    Add another award to the award list. It is just the standard add method for a List object, overwritten in order to maintain the award list always in ascending order by award value.
